text: Input/Output Data Input/Output data is the type of data that an agent both recognizes and delivers. The Excel Decoder agent consumes bytearray types and delivers ExcelUDR s. Meta Information Model (MIM) The Excel Decoder agent only publishes and accesses MIMs of general type.
title: Excel Decoder Agent Input/Output Data and MIM - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
